---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="reviews">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2
        class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-4xl"
      >
        Real Experiences, Real Success
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mx-auto max-w-2xl">
        Hear how our tools are helping professionals transform their job search
        and career development.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8 space-y-8">
      <div
        class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center mb-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
              Rajesh Kumar
            </h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">
              Software Engineer, Bangalore
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-black dark:text-white">
          The Job Analysis tool gave me incredible insights into tech job market
          trends. I discovered salary ranges, key skills, and hidden
          requirements that I was missing in my previous applications.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center mb-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
              Priya Sharma
            </h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">
              Marketing Specialist, Mumbai
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-black dark:text-white">
          The Resume Tailor feature is a game-changer. It helped me optimize my
          resume for ATS systems and highlight the most relevant skills for each
          job application. My interview calls increased significantly!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center mb-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
              Arjun Patel
            </h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">
              Product Manager, Hyderabad
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-black dark:text-white">
          I was struggling to write compelling cover letters. The Cover Letter
          Generator helped me create professional, role-specific letters
          quickly. I could choose between professional, creative, and startup
          styles to match different company cultures.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center mb-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
              Neha Reddy
            </h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">
              Data Scientist, Chennai
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-black dark:text-white">
          The Job Analysis tool provided invaluable insights into tech industry
          trends, including salary ranges and essential skills, enhancing my
          applications.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center mb-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
              Vikram Singh
            </h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">
              Management Consultant, Delhi
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-black dark:text-white">
          Switching between industries can be challenging. The Resume Tailor and
          Cover Letter Generator helped me reposition my skills for different
          roles, making my applications more targeted and effective.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-center mb-4">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
              Aisha Khan
            </h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">
              Startup Founder, Pune
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-black dark:text-white">
          As a founder, understanding talent is crucial. The Job Analysis tool
          provides deep market insights, helping me understand skill trends and
          make informed hiring decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
